===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr}} {{term|république|république|republic|lang=fr}}, derived from {{etyl|la}} {{term|res publica|rēs publica|republic|lang=la}}, from {{term|res|rēs|thing|lang=la}} + {{term|publicus|pūblica|public|lang=la}}; hence literally “the public thing”.

